      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm buying my first house and i'm a bit confused. what actually is escrow and what happens to my earnest money while we wait for the closing date?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey, i'm buying my first house and i'm a bit confused. what actually is escrow and what happens to my earnest money while we wait for the closing date?",
