      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry, what did you mean by the goblin thing? i'm just trying to understand the legal/financial side of this. can you just explain the actual responsibilities of the escrow agent without the metaphors?",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
